<br />
<br />What I am talking is the format of the 8x8 Tiles and Attributes for such formats, They do differ.
<br />
<br />This is not really a rushed thread, But one question remains, If there are no other formats besides NES supported, Why even bother?
<br />
<br />And yes, I can still disassemble 6502 quite well.

		

